About:
======

This package contains a subset of the PLASMA software library,
https://bitbucket.org/icl/plasma
Selected functions are ported from the OpenMP to the StarPU
task-based runtime.
The code has been tested with GNU C compiler.

Building the library:
=====================

1. Prepare a
    make.inc
   file corresponding to your setting. A good practice is to edit
   the provided template
    make.inc.example

2. Build the project by running
    make

Running the tests:
==================

3. Run the tests by
    cd testing-intertwine
    ./plasma_testing_intertwine.py

Contact:
